					<div class="post">
				<h3>New beta: ahl_watersedgeb4</h3>
				<div class="date"><img src="./styles/new-life/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" />Posted: <strong>Thu Dec 11, 2008 3:29 am</strong></div>
				<div class="author">by <strong>Varinger</strong></div>
				<div class="content">I've been working on this one a while, off and on and off and so on.<br /><br />Title: Water's Edge<br /><br />Description:<br /><br />A small snackshop, run as a front for the mafia.<br /><br /><br />Gameplay notes:<br /><br />Pretty small.  It centers on one modest shop.<br /><br />I made some alternate gameplay entities, so that if you play with goals off, the shop is easily accessible, and if you play with goals enabled, the shop is in a lockdown mode, with only the front doors and duct access being unshuttered.  You can still break in through the other windows and rear door, but you'll have to make some noise and/or waste some ammo to do so.  Enabling goalplay doesn't change the default Teamplay-style gameplay.  It's still a matter of splattering the other team, one life per player.<br /><br />Instructions on how to activate one mode or the other are included in the readme.<br /><br />Download: <a href="http://www.ghgmapdepot.com/maps/ahl_watersedgeb4.zip" class="postlink">ahl_watersedgeb4</a></div>
			</div>
